Functional Requirements

- Monitor the (mock) Snowy Mountain Hydro Scheme and provide the services to the various demands placed on the scheme.
- There are demands for water and there are demands for power.

Subsystems

-Generator
--Input
   Channel water flow.
   Power.
--Output
   Power.
   Channel water flow extraction.

-Dam
--Input
   Channel/s.
   River/s.
--Output
   River/s.
   Channel/s.
--Requirement
   Monitor the water levels in the dam.
--Design


Interface

Channel

